    "Thou shalt not speak with deceit nor harbor guile in thy heart.",
    "Let thy words be as pure as the waters of Eden, and let truth be the mantle that adorns thy soul.",
    "Thou shalt not indulge in wrath or hold onto anger against thy kin.",
    "Seek reconciliation and pursue peace, for in forgiveness lies the path to righteousness.",
    "Thou shalt not despoil the earth, the seas, nor the skies, for the Lord has entrusted them unto your care."
